snippet.title: Outfit Teaser: Teyvat Style – Silhouettes of the Night | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Under the dim night sky, spots of bright light flicker faintly.
Is it the burning flames of the warrior's sword? Or the swaying stars on the Prinzessin's dress?
Or maybe it's neither. Those flashes of light are but a herald of a new dawn.
